.. warning::
    Current status is "experimental".

``scrapy-po`` implements Page Object pattern for Scrapy.

License is BSD 3-clause.

Installation
============

::

    pip install scrapy-po

scrapy-po requires Python >= 3.6 and Scrapy 1.7+.

